&lt;h2 id=&quot;toc_25&quot;&gt;tl;dr&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This isn&amp;#39;t for the faint of heart. If you skipped to down here, you should probably just download the &lt;a href=&quot;http://code.google.com/p/git-osx-installer/&quot;&gt;Git OS X Installer&lt;/a&gt; package (generally one maintenance release behind latest), or use MacPorts or Homebrew both of which are current to the latest stable release of Git.&lt;/p&gt;

